sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 👤 Developer
    participant AI as 🤖 Copilot

    rect rgb(45, 106, 79, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 🟢 SESSION START
        Dev->>AI: Load context: SPEC.md, ROADMAP.md, *_PLAN.md
        AI-->>Dev: ✅ Context confirmed, current status understood
    end

    rect rgb(106, 61, 154, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 🔄 FEATURE LOOP
        Dev->>AI: Create FEATURE_ANALYSIS.md for feature
        AI-->>Dev: 📊 Analysis with options, pros/cons, recommendation
        Dev->>AI: Choose Option X -> Create FEATURE_PLAN.md
        AI-->>Dev: 📝 Phased plan with steps + checklist
    end

    rect rgb(2, 62, 138, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: ⚙️ IMPLEMENTATION LOOP
        Dev->>AI: Implement Phase N from PLAN
        AI-->>Dev: 💻 Code changes
        Dev->>AI: Test / Validate
        alt ✅ Pass
            AI-->>Dev: Phase N validated
        else ❌ Issue Found
            Dev->>AI: Describe problem
            AI-->>Dev: 🐛 ISSUE.md (diagnosis, fix, recommendations)
            Dev->>AI: Re-implement fix
            AI-->>Dev: 💻 Fixed code
        end
    end

    rect rgb(191, 54, 12, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 📚 DOCUMENTATION
        Dev->>AI: Update CHANGELOG.md + README.md
        AI-->>Dev: 📄 Updated docs
    end

    rect rgb(230, 81, 0, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 🔧 REFACTORING (after big changes / multiple features)
        Dev->>AI: Analyze codebase, create SCOPE_REFACTOR.md
        AI-->>Dev: 🔧 Duplication, wrappers, dead code, complexity findings
        Dev->>AI: Implement Priority 1 refactoring items
        AI-->>Dev: 💻 Refactored code (tests passing)
    end

    rect rgb(21, 101, 192, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 📦 PUBLISH (when ready to release)
        Dev->>AI: Create PUBLISH.md targeting GitHub/GitLab
        AI-->>Dev: 📦 Audit: missing docs, tests, secrets, CI, licensing
        Dev->>AI: Fix blockers from PUBLISH.md
        AI-->>Dev: ✅ All checklist items resolved
    end

    rect rgb(56, 142, 60, 0.15)
        Note over Dev,AI: 🔴 SESSION END
        Dev->>AI: Summarize session, update checklists
        AI-->>Dev: ✅ ROADMAP.md checklist updated, summary provided
    end
